longBusinessSummary: Legend Power Systems Inc., together with its subsidiaries, operates as an electrical energy conservation company in Canada and the United States. The company assembles, markets, and sells SmartGATE, a patented device that enables dynamic power management of commercial or industrial Buildings. Legend Power Systems Inc. was founded in 1987 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
